    Aracnia, sitting in the conference room contacted Quickstrike. "All right 
Commander, come to Destructors base with PAralysis and the rat. Remember to 
leave the shields up and the autoguns armed. Theres no point in not having 
them armed." She then turned to Kitkat.
    
    Megatron inhaled deeply as he entered. There was something about this 
room....mabey something IN this room that gave him an uneasy feeling. He felt 
himself shiver. "Kitkat, can we get on with it please? The longer we take 
here.....the more of a chance Zardus has to prepare himself."
